  "body": "<p>It's been busy around here - there's a fun announcement coming on Thursday! It's something <a href=\"http://kellypurkey.typepad.com/\">Kelly</a> &amp; I have been working on for months and months and are extremely excited about sharing with all of you. Since I love snapping photos of my process (these are all taken with my iPhone), I thought I would share with you how this layout came together.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598761479498-E817EAF0BTNFG69JN79F/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598761497188-KNK80XMHK28FBWDB8ABN/3b-20140309-065907.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>By cutting the squares in half, a perfectly sized triangle is made!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"3c-20140309-065916.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598761531784-6GC149G4UGC0325CL7T3/3c-20140309-065916.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"3d-20140309-065928.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598761531889-AH1BAE3ZV10YVG74ASQF/3d-20140309-065928.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"3e-20140309-065938.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598761532661-XU90S2B2G0R2UQMZC7W6/3e-20140309-065938.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3f-20140309-065950.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598761532661-8J17ANBJ7D4BYPYYVUTD/3f-20140309-065950.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3g-20140309-070014.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598761533242-PO7PYX63OCHF8OSNN6GD/3g-20140309-070014.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3h-20140309-070027.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598761533316-MEF2PF4NN5F5CLNYLJTX/3h-20140309-070027.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3i-20140309-070054.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598761533846-5MEVR6LA97RWJ0QJGYFJ/3i-20140309-070054.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3j-20140309-070108.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598761533983-G3VTE1LHFFLPG32NOQVO/3j-20140309-070108.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3k-we-are-the-lucky-ones.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598761537122-AL32L1H1LMS2TZFMSKTE/3k-we-are-the-lucky-ones.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Shop for our latest products online at Two Peas In A Bucket and <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=simon%20home%20page&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom\">Simon Says Stamp</a> and <a href=\"http://www.hsn.com/search?query=amy%20tangerine\">HSN</a>!</p>"
